1 MR. PAGLIUCA: And, your Honor, may I continue reading?
2 THE COURT: What lines?

5 Through what line?
6 MR. PAGLIUCA: Five, your Honor.
7 THE COURT: Okay. Go ahead.
8 MS. COMEY: I would object, your Honor.
9 THE COURT: I'm sorry?
10 MS. COMEY: Same objection, your Honor.
11 THE COURT: Go ahead.
12 BY MR. PAGLIUCA:
13 Q. (Reading)
14 "Q. Do you know what I mean by sexual intercourse or do I need to go through the various acts?
15 "A. Oh, I am pretty sure I know what sexual intercourse is being I have two children.
16 "Q. Well, I just want to make sure we're clear about some things. Did Mr. Epstein ever insert his penis into any part of your body at all?
17 "A. I just said that I've never had any sexual intercourse with Mr. Epstein, and that I knew what -- "
18 THE COURT: You misread.
19 BY MR. PAGLIUCA:
20 SOUTHERN DISTRICT REPORTERS, P.C. (212) 805-0300
21 DOJ-OGR-00013247
